OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor 'revolting' stretch    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmarks                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Strictly Come Dancing's Shirley Ballas 
OL,6, has revealed she was told her stretch  
OL,7, marks were "revolting" by a dance      
OL,8, judge, six weeks after giving birth.   
OL,10,F"It wasn't like it is today where      
OL,11,Feverybody's got to walk on an eggshell 
OL,12,Fto tell you something," the 63-year-old
OL,13,Ftold the Radio Times podcast.          
OL,15,F"I went back to dancing six weeks after
OL,16,Fhaving my baby.                        
OL,18,F"I was told: 'I marked you third as I  
OL,19,Frefuse to look at the stretch marks on 
OL,20,Fyour back. I find it revolting.'"      
